Class User

java.lang.Object
entityClasses.User
public class User extends Object

Title: User Class

Description: This User class represents a user entity in the system. It contains the user's details such as userName, password, and roles being played.

    • User

      public User(String userName, String password, String OTP, String fn, String mn, String ln, String pfn, String ea, boolean r1, boolean r2, boolean r3, boolean tpw)

      Method: User(String userName, String password, String OTP, String fn, String mn, String ln, String pfn, String ea, boolean r1, boolean r2, boolean r3, boolean tpw)

      Description: This constructor is used to establish user entity objects.

      Parameters:
      userName - specifies the account userName for this user
      password - specifies the account password for this user
      OTP - specifies the one time password for this user
      fn - specifies the first name for this user
      mn - specifies the middle name for this user
      ln - specifies the last name for this user
      pfn - specifies the preferred first name for this user
      ea - specifies the email address for this user
      r1 - specifies the the Admin attribute (TRUE or FALSE) for this user
      r2 - specifies the the Student attribute (TRUE or FALSE) for this user
      r3 - specifies the the Reviewer attribute (TRUE or FALSE) for this user
      tpw - specifies the temp password for this user
